data.description: Welcome to Windrow at the Cove, and welcome home to this beautifully upgraded two-story home. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a generous 1963 square feet of living space, an open-concept living area seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen spaces. The kitchen has been thoughtfully upgraded with espresso-finished cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The kitchen island with a breakfast bar provides a central gathering place for casual meals, and a pantry closet ensures ample storage for all your culinary needs. For those who love to entertain, the covered patio directly off the kitchen is ideal for hosting memorable dinner parties or simply enjoying a peaceful evening outdoors. The oversized primary suite upstairs boasts a separate sitting area to unwind and relax. The en-suite bath features a soaking jetted tub, a walk-in shower, dual vanity sinks, and a spacious walk-in closet. An ADA staircasing that can stay or be removed. The community clubhouse offers a junior Olympic pool, a well-equipped fitness center, and shaded BBQ areas where you can gather with friends and family. Take advantage of this opportunity to own a truly exceptional home in the sought-after Windrow at the Cove community.
